title: Thomas' slam puts Guardians by Tigers, into ALCS
description: Lane Thomas hit a grand slam off Tarik Skubal and Cleveland beat the Detroit Tigers 7-3 in Game 5 of their AL Division Series, moving the Guardians into another postseason matchup against the Yankees. Game 1 of the ALCS is Monday in the Bronx.
author: Jesse Rogers

title: Beterbiev edges Bivol to become undisputed champion
description: Artur Beterbiev beat Dmitry Bivol by majority decision to become undisputed light-heavyweight world champion in a high-quality contest in Saudi.

title: 'More late Scotland anguish as Clarke fights cynicism & scepticism'
description: Steve Clarke was denied a tangible and much-needed piece of optimism as Croatia inflicted Scotland's latest honourable defeat, writes Tom English.

title: Wardley sensationally knocks out Clarke in first round of rematch
description: Fabio Wardley knocked out Frazer Clarke in the first round to retain the British and Commonwealth heavyweight titles.

title: Whittaker injured after flipping out of ring as Cameron fight declared draw
description: Ben Whittaker and Liam Cameron collided and collapsed over the top rope in the fifth round of their 10-round light-heavyweight contest as it ended early in a split-decision draw.
